{"tid":933667,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉貼)大嶼山 葵青喺1514年俾葡國佔領7年 叫Tamão 仲早過澳門43年","createTime":"2018-12-08T16:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T00:38:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ac075e790599e3d49dae29ae74cc7beeaa3d54","tid":933667,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:26:15.000Z","msg":"現代西方社會首度與中土接觸，原來早喺1493年明朝，葡萄牙和阿爾加爾維王國（阿維斯王朝）軍隊抵達大明帝國東莞守禦千所的領地（今深圳及香港沿海)。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來英國人統治香港前嘅300年，葡人曾一度佔領大嶼山 葵青！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1514年，歐維士（Jorge &Aacute;lvares）率領一支葡萄牙船隊到達珠江三角洲，發出登陸貿易的要求，明朝政府不予接納，因而只能在水面上與華商貿易。<span style=\"color: red;\">同年，塞克拉（Diogo Lopes de Sequeira）再率領葡萄牙船隊佔領「屯門海澳」，並在其上刻立佔領石碑，修築工事，設刑場、製火器</span>。<br />\n<br />\n1515－1517年間，葡萄牙人因貿易問題與明帝國起糾紛。1517年6月17日，葡萄牙使者皮萊資（Tom&eacute; Perez）領費爾南&middot;佩雷茲&middot;德&middot;安德拉德（Fern&atilde;o Perez de Andrade）等人所統領的八船船隊前往珠江一帶，並於8月15日抵達「屯門島」。<span style=\"color: blue;\">「屯門島」應是指今香港的大嶼山</span> ，也有人認為是指內伶仃島或大鏟島。<br />\n<br />\n1518年，費爾南之弟西眇（Sim&atilde;o D. Andrade）率領葡船一艘、帆船三艘抵達屯門，並在鄰近島嶼建設堡壘壕障，設置刑場，並肆意掠奪，拒絕明朝課稅。葡萄牙人企圖進一步攻佔南山半島(今深圳市南山區蛇口)，但由於明帝國駐軍太多而失敗，徹退至「屯門島」安營紮寨，作下一步軍事準備。此後，<span style=\"color: purple;\">葡人又在「屯門海澳」及「葵涌海澳」（今香港青衣島、葵涌一帶）探查據點，製火器，立石碑</span>，並與當地居民衝突。<br />\n<br />\n1521年，明帝國嘉靖帝派遣廣東海道副使汪鋐進攻葡佔屯門(Tam&atilde;o)。最後明軍獲勝。至此，明帝國接管了「屯門島」、「屯門海澳」及「葵涌海澳」等葡佔屯門全境。葡萄牙人自此再也未能重奪在香港的失地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/06/2zyLQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2F2zyLQK.jpg&h=9038bb44&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">點解先生無教嘅？又好似無任何史蹟留下咁嘅？</span></span>"},{"pid":"1775b25419ad4709d3891eb77a28c107e3bd281b","tid":933667,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/therootshk/photos/a.413539545760214/417469468700555/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftherootshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.413539545760214%2F417469468700555%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=8SOQvrIox0hGW%2BDb74PY28mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=58d600f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/therootshk/photos/a.413539545760214/417469468700555/?type=3&amp;theater</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/12/06/c4lCak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F12%2F06%2Fc4lCak.jpg&h=649ba0de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6993022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6993022&d=8SOQvrIox0hGW%2BDb74PY28mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=d0be696f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6993022</a>"},{"pid":"0866a09dcdf380586c975a222b897db376b68f0d","tid":933667,"uid":22675,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"屯門自古以來都是葡萄牙王國不可分裂的一部分"},{"pid":"ea3f816e99507b403d1226e115922e3c660ed9fe","tid":933667,"uid":22675,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"大航海時代<img src=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/faces/sg/bouncy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Ffaces%2Fsg%2Fbouncy.gif&h=bf978b2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c635a8d6effbe5401286832a322857bf58ec3a1","tid":933667,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ff2636bf40b78a5afd01f83dce7b181f8e5b16","tid":933667,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T19:01:08.000Z","msg":"自古以來？"},{"pid":"cac513f4a2969efd2df25bd79297a848e87e40b1","tid":933667,"uid":35752,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T20:28:48.000Z","msg":"隱約記得以前中三西史老師講過下屯門海戰<br />\n提子國啲船仔唔夠明國啲老翻大炮抽<br />\n有好多中西貿易嘅topics<br />\n<br />\n中史教明朝就提都唔撚提下<br />\n淨係叫你背下啲乜乜之治呀宦官參政呀邊條撚樣三十年唔上朝呀嗰啲廢鳩嘢<br />\n<br />\n中學西史科令你可以清楚知道到西方同東方各發生咩事<br />\n科技貿易文化史都有啲<br />\n中學中史科基本上只係皇室歷史, 不停重複tvb d 19劇情"},{"pid":"ee4a62168fd336a0fda2453d8d4df1519b7ce627","tid":933667,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T21:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"054a72a6ab27586ccfd1a62de41f3788d6feb896","tid":933667,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:17:21.000Z","msg":"give me an Portugal passport<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a448db747531d53f43f33f87846be2a706f0598b","tid":933667,"uid":2429,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T01:03:19.000Z","msg":"C朗都係我哋中國人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5119120e3e96cafa7b5fef16b7ba2bb8dbcaaec","tid":933667,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"不嬲都話學世史，而且一直都應該睇由西方學者編撰嘅中史"},{"pid":"2876fdff2545aac33dd02b9c54c3a6b584ed9fc8","tid":933667,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"Her&oacute;is do Mar nobre povo <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9c492f4db8e55a4f1219166e222e378935d3ac","tid":933667,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"認袓歸宗 英國長期同盟國葡萄牙 <br />\n做葡人也好 做英人也好 就是不做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DdOEpfypWQA?t=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.l